Where's talent?
We have 5 seconds.

02:15.208 --> 02:16.875
- And the letters?
- It's fine.

02:17.083 --> 02:19.042
Did you get that in shot?

02:19.292 --> 02:20.792
Okay, where's Hal?

02:21.000 --> 02:23.417
I can only hold it
a few seconds.

02:23.625 --> 02:26.583
Get the first team on set.
The letters are fading.

02:26.792 --> 02:28.292
Come on, we gotta go!

02:28.500 --> 02:30.083
- She looks great. Come!
- I'm ready.

02:30.333 --> 02:31.708
- Please.
- Let's go.

02:31.917 --> 02:33.333
Quick review, Nicole.

02:33.625 --> 02:36.000
Get out of the
car, run across...

02:36.250 --> 02:37.917
you see the
skywriting, "Help"...

02:38.125 --> 02:39.792
and realise everything's
gone wrong.

02:40.042 --> 02:42.625
It's incredible.
You had it all figured out.

02:42.833 --> 02:44.833
And now it's all chaos.

02:45.083 --> 02:47.667
You need to
project despair.

02:48.125 --> 02:50.792
- We gotta go. We're losing...
- I know.

02:51.083 --> 02:54.667
Make me feel the
whole human condition.

02:54.917 --> 02:56.417
- You know?
- Lock it up!

03:00.542 --> 03:03.208
Can you stop the drill
for 5 minutes?

03:03.500 --> 03:04.750
What's that, "Help"?

03:05.083 --> 03:06.917
- Roll camera!
- Camera's rolling.

03:07.208 --> 03:08.583
- Speed!
- Higher.

03:08.792 --> 03:10.875
Scene 121, take 1!

03:11.625 --> 03:12.667
Action!

03:15.042 --> 03:17.417
Faster, faster.

03:17.708 --> 03:19.458
You're like a zombie!

03:19.667 --> 03:22.250
Okay, hit the mark.
Look up.

03:22.583 --> 03:25.167
Come on, come on.
And good, good.

03:25.375 --> 03:26.625
Cut! We cut!

03:27.000 --> 03:29.042
Nicole, thank you.

03:29.333 --> 03:31.458
That was amazing.
So compelling.

03:31.708 --> 03:35.250
Your body language, it's
so emotional, everything you do.

03:35.458 --> 03:38.750
You get the big bucks because
you make me look great.

03:38.958 --> 03:41.417
Camp David here.
About the ring.

03:41.625 --> 03:43.000
Mary, here's Nicole.

03:45.208 --> 03:48.250
- Sorry to bug you.
- Okay, pal.

03:48.500 --> 03:50.375
- Do I sign the thing?
- Voucher.

03:50.583 --> 03:51.417
Sure.

03:51.625 --> 03:53.042
You get a voucher?

03:53.292 --> 03:55.042
- Did they get it?
- Let's hope.

03:55.250 --> 03:57.875
Our wardrobe, right?
John, take this.

03:58.083 --> 04:01.167
Where do I know you from?
I know you, right?

04:01.500 --> 04:02.458
Thanks.

04:03.458 --> 04:06.292
Chippers in So-Ho.
I waited on you.

04:06.667 --> 04:08.250
What a great memory!

04:08.500 --> 04:11.292
It was a couple
of months ago, right?

04:11.500 --> 04:14.083
But I remembered your face.

04:14.708 --> 04:16.375
And you're an actress.

04:16.583 --> 04:17.750
I'm an extra.

04:17.958 --> 04:19.416
A face in the crowd.

04:19.708 --> 04:21.583
I'll get my sweatshirt.

04:24.083 --> 04:25.917
When do you finish work?

04:28.667 --> 04:32.000
Was that gorgeous black girl
you came with your girlfriend?

04:32.792 --> 04:36.125
It was a guy in drag!
What are you talking about?

04:36.458 --> 04:38.875
- Gorgeous girlfriend?
- Beautiful, whatever it was.

04:39.083 --> 04:41.917
I was writing a
piece on transvestites...

04:42.125 --> 04:44.958
which is why you saw my
"gorgeous girlfriend".

04:45.167 --> 04:47.458
Well if you ever come back...

04:47.667 --> 04:49.625
I get off around midnight.

04:55.208 --> 04:56.500
You need a...

04:57.833 --> 04:59.833
Excuse me, can I borrow...?

05:00.917 --> 05:02.792
Tell me how close I am.

05:03.000 --> 05:05.292
You're from rich parents...

05:05.542 --> 05:09.042
you see a shrink and
you're dyslexic, right?

05:09.292 --> 05:10.375
Thanks.

05:12.292 --> 05:14.375
- That was good.
- I try.

05:14.625 --> 05:16.250
My father's wealthy...

05:16.500 --> 05:18.167
I do see a shrink...

05:18.375 --> 05:21.750
and I'm insomniac,
so you're in the ballpark.

05:22.000 --> 05:24.500
I remember you had
an amazing look.

05:24.708 --> 05:26.667
And I thought,
"Trouble for someone."

05:26.875 --> 05:28.792
I think I dreamt about you.

05:29.000 --> 05:30.708
Really, I remember
your face.

05:30.917 --> 05:32.292
Who wouldn't?

05:32.500 --> 05:34.250
Please, sign your voucher.

05:38.167 --> 05:39.167
Thanks.

05:43.792 --> 05:45.708
- Lee!
- Excuse me.

05:45.917 --> 05:46.875
Over here.

05:47.208 --> 05:50.458
Sandy, you'll send the
truffles to the president, right?

05:50.708 --> 05:53.542
Tomorrow at 7, okay?
In the park.

05:53.750 --> 05:55.083
- Thanks.
- Here he is.

05:55.667 --> 05:58.125
Sorry.
Ready for our tête-à-tête?

05:58.375 --> 06:00.625
Absolutely.
Everything in hand.

06:00.875 --> 06:02.458
- Bill Gaines.
- How are you?

06:02.667 --> 06:04.250
Nicole's press agent.

06:04.458 --> 06:07.167
Please, let's not
dwell on the bulimia.

06:07.375 --> 06:10.417
Believe me, Bill,
this is about lots of things.

06:10.625 --> 06:12.625
You said you'd show me
where you grew up.

06:12.833 --> 06:14.083
I did, I promised.

06:25.500 --> 06:28.375
It's great we could do this.
Makes a big difference.

06:28.583 --> 06:30.875
So kind of you
to show me.

06:31.083 --> 06:33.583
This stuff makes a
lot of people nervous.

06:40.167 --> 06:42.000
Sorry to disturb you.

06:42.458 --> 06:44.292
This lady lived here...

06:45.292 --> 06:47.125
as a child, years ago.

06:47.375 --> 06:50.000
Nicole Oliver. You must know
her. Great actress.

06:50.250 --> 06:51.500
What d'you want?

06:51.750 --> 06:54.750
He's writing an article
about me...

06:54.958 --> 06:57.083
and I'd like to show him
where I used to live.

06:57.333 --> 07:00.875
Five minutes. It'd be
great for the magazine.

07:01.083 --> 07:02.417
Come in and look around.

07:02.625 --> 07:04.500
- I appreciate it.
- Thank you.

07:05.000 --> 07:07.042
Look how tiny her feet are.

07:07.292 --> 07:09.250
Like, this is
where it all began.

07:09.500 --> 07:11.542
Did you have
feet like that, too?

07:15.083 --> 07:16.750
Strange for you, I guess.

07:17.458 --> 07:20.208
- It's changed, I think.
- I hope so.

07:20.458 --> 07:22.042
It feels smaller.

07:22.333 --> 07:24.500
Small?
That often happens.

07:24.750 --> 07:26.625
How long have you lived here?

07:27.375 --> 07:30.208
Never mind. Can
we go upstairs?

07:30.417 --> 07:32.042
- Terrific.
- Whatever you want.

07:32.292 --> 07:33.917
- Is that okay?
- She said okay.

07:34.125 --> 07:36.250
- I don't care.
- Great. Thank you.

07:39.167 --> 07:41.750
I had this whole wall
plastered...

07:42.125 --> 07:46.042
with movie star photos. I dreamt
about being in a movie...

07:47.333 --> 07:48.750
with Warren Beatty.

07:48.958 --> 07:50.708
You had nice dreams.

07:52.625 --> 07:56.708
And I'd lie on the bed naked
and watch my body develop.

07:58.292 --> 07:59.167
"Naked..."

07:59.417 --> 08:01.083
And I prayed that...

08:01.667 --> 08:04.708
my breasts and legs
would be beautiful...

08:04.958 --> 08:07.250
so I could be
an actress.

08:08.000 --> 08:11.667
You cut a very
erotic figure like that.

08:12.083 --> 08:13.708
I have to say it.

08:15.708 --> 08:18.250
Fortunately I matured quickly.

08:18.500 --> 08:21.750
I remember my brothers
spying on me...

08:22.000 --> 08:25.833
in the shower, or they
rubbed up against me.

08:27.583 --> 08:30.958
I empathise with them
totally. I really...

08:31.250 --> 08:32.250
Please.

08:33.000 --> 08:34.207
No?

08:34.707 --> 08:36.707
- Married.
- Happily?

08:36.917 --> 08:38.125
Very.

08:39.957 --> 08:41.917
But you have to work at it.

08:42.125 --> 08:45.000
You have to, if you want
fidelity in a relationship.

08:46.125 --> 08:50.042
But have you ever given
in to lust in this room...

08:50.292 --> 08:52.958
and really let
yourself go...

08:53.208 --> 08:54.458
in a big way?

08:57.667 --> 08:59.625
I can't sleep
with you.

08:59.833 --> 09:03.375
You can't, I know that.
But I had to...

09:04.208 --> 09:05.625
The proximity is...

09:05.958 --> 09:07.083
thrilling...

09:07.292 --> 09:08.875
and irresistible.

09:09.083 --> 09:12.292
- Not that you're not attractive.
- Very kind.

09:12.542 --> 09:14.417
I find you very attractive.

09:14.667 --> 09:18.458
But some things I won't do,
out of commitment.

09:18.708 --> 09:20.917
I hear you. You
don't have to...

09:21.125 --> 09:25.167
I only have intercourse
with my husband, Phil.

09:26.417 --> 09:28.583
My body belongs
to my husband.

09:28.792 --> 09:30.750
Listen, I understand...

09:31.125 --> 09:35.083
But from the neck up,
that's another story.

09:46.167 --> 09:50.167
After your nomination you formed
a production company, right?

09:50.417 --> 09:53.750
Right. You have to develop
your own projects.

09:53.958 --> 09:58.083
You can't imagine the
amount of crap I get sent.

09:58.333 --> 10:00.750
Plus, I'd really like
to direct one day.

10:00.958 --> 10:03.375
Really? Well,
I don't want to be pushy...

10:03.583 --> 10:06.667
but I've got a screenplay
I've written...

10:06.875 --> 10:09.083
and today I thought
it might be...

10:09.292 --> 10:11.917
you know, perfect
for you.

10:12.167 --> 10:15.458
Really. Right now
it's written for a man...

10:15.708 --> 10:19.708
but it could easily be
rewritten for a woman.

10:20.125 --> 10:21.208
What's it about?

10:21.417 --> 10:24.917
An armoured car robbery,
but with a personal crisis.

10:25.167 --> 10:28.875
- Who would I play?
- One of the guards.

10:29.375 --> 10:32.542
It needs a rewrite, with
a feminist statement.

10:32.750 --> 10:34.292
I know you're politically active...

10:34.500 --> 10:37.750
and I think it could
work so well.

10:37.958 --> 10:40.667
I've been working
on it for a year...

10:40.875 --> 10:43.667
and I can't progress
unless a star is involved.

10:43.917 --> 10:46.125
And someone like you, it'd be...

10:46.333 --> 10:48.375
Have you given it to
any actors?

10:48.583 --> 10:51.833
Yeah, but their agents reject
it before they see it...

10:52.042 --> 10:54.792
because I have no track
record as a screenwriter...

10:55.000 --> 10:58.375
although the script gets a
terrific reaction.

10:59.042 --> 11:01.833
- Let me think about it.
- Really?

11:02.125 --> 11:04.750
Great, because I don't want to...

11:05.125 --> 11:07.875
- But I think you'd enjoy it.
- Let me think about it.

11:08.167 --> 11:09.083
Sure.

11:26.500 --> 11:28.875
He's coming!
Come this way!

11:29.125 --> 11:30.542
Come this way, everyone!

11:30.750 --> 11:32.292
It's him. Come on.

11:32.833 --> 11:36.375
We watch you every
Sunday on TV!

11:36.708 --> 11:39.042
We wouldn't miss it
for the world!

11:39.250 --> 11:40.667
Good to see you.

11:40.875 --> 11:43.125
- Will you stay long?
- As long as I can.

11:43.333 --> 11:46.417
Father Gladden is
our guest, from the TV.

11:46.625 --> 11:50.292
Father, my daughter got a prize
at school for charity work.

11:50.542 --> 11:52.792
She'd love to have
your autograph.

11:53.000 --> 11:54.542
Entrance into the
Kingdom of God...

11:54.750 --> 11:58.042
is determined by our response
to the neighbour in need.

11:58.250 --> 12:00.042
I don't know what I'm doing here.

12:00.250 --> 12:03.083
Relax, I was the
same at first.

12:03.375 --> 12:07.083
My room's so spare.
And with a Bible!

12:07.417 --> 12:08.792
And the water comes out brown.

12:09.042 --> 12:12.333
I told the handyman. Really,
I know what you're going through.

12:12.583 --> 12:15.500
When my husband went off
with his secretary, I was lost.

12:15.750 --> 12:18.542
Someone said,
"You were raised a Catholic.

12:18.833 --> 12:22.750
How could you consider a hit man?"
And I heard about this retreat.

12:22.958 --> 12:24.625
- But I'm not religious.
- Nor am I.

12:24.833 --> 12:28.458
My life, religious? I've had
two divorces and two abortions.

12:28.792 --> 12:32.292
But to take a break from
the chaos of the city...

12:32.542 --> 12:33.750
No, no, no.

12:33.958 --> 12:36.250
The water comes out
brown in my room.

12:36.458 --> 12:38.417
And the bed's hard.

12:38.667 --> 12:42.458
You've had a trauma.
No therapy, no pills...

12:42.875 --> 12:44.750
what you need is peace and quiet.

12:45.083 --> 12:47.167
Your emotions
have to settle.

12:48.667 --> 12:52.167
I couldn't go back
to teaching again.

12:52.458 --> 12:53.667
Simplify.

12:54.042 --> 12:57.167
Who's more popular,
the Pope or Elvis?

12:57.417 --> 12:59.250
- I don't think there's any doubt...
- Elvis!

13:00.875 --> 13:04.375
Do you think that the Beatles,
at the height of their fame...

13:04.667 --> 13:06.583
were bigger stars than Jesus?

13:06.792 --> 13:09.750
- World population was smaller...
- Autograph, please?

13:10.250 --> 13:12.875
The food's the worst.
What is this?

13:13.083 --> 13:16.000
I don't know. Shoe leather?
You don't have to eat it.

13:16.250 --> 13:17.667
I asked for it rare.

13:17.958 --> 13:19.583
But you don't like meat.

13:19.833 --> 13:22.292
I said "rare".
You heard me.

13:22.542 --> 13:24.958
I told them twice.
"Not overdone."

13:25.167 --> 13:28.542
Well, we're not
here to enjoy ourselves.

13:29.833 --> 13:31.625
Eat it, or something else.

13:33.375 --> 13:37.292
- The macaroni cheese is good.
- Would you like mine? It's rare.

13:38.458 --> 13:40.875
- That's nice of you.
- Please!

13:41.167 --> 13:42.125
You sure?

13:43.500 --> 13:47.375
You see, I can't eat
steak that's not rare.

13:47.917 --> 13:49.792
Doesn't that look nice!

13:50.250 --> 13:51.875
I started as a hobby...

13:52.083 --> 13:55.417
but I get so many orders now,
I can't make them quick enough.

13:55.625 --> 13:57.375
All genuine ceramic.

13:57.583 --> 14:00.375
And this rubber
bulb here...

14:00.667 --> 14:04.417
that you fill with
washable red dye.

14:04.625 --> 14:08.042
One squeeze and His
wounds bleed. Watch that.

14:08.292 --> 14:09.708
Isn't that something?

14:10.792 --> 14:12.750
- Do you like the country?
- Oh, very much.

14:12.958 --> 14:15.625
I went to a Catholic school,
you know?

14:15.875 --> 14:18.708
So I have moments of
nostalgia for the faith.

14:20.417 --> 14:22.083
Let your soul wander.

14:22.375 --> 14:24.333
And if the miracles
of nature...

14:24.583 --> 14:27.708
lead to intimations of
something larger...

14:28.125 --> 14:30.792
try and have
an open heart.

14:31.708 --> 14:35.792
Are there ticks here?
I'd hate to get Lyme's disease.

14:36.000 --> 14:38.417
- No casualties so far.
- Good.

14:38.625 --> 14:40.125
Could you excuse me?

14:40.417 --> 14:41.708
Yes. Bye.

14:53.417 --> 14:54.708
<i>What, a divorce?</i>

14:55.000 --> 14:56.250
<i>A divorce.</i>

14:56.792 --> 14:59.000
- Try and understand.
- Why?

14:59.208 --> 15:02.708
It's not you, it's me.
I have to...

15:02.958 --> 15:04.875
- Pull over!
- Robin, we should...

15:05.083 --> 15:06.250
Pull the fucking car over!

15:06.500 --> 15:08.333
Jesus, will you calm down?

15:14.375 --> 15:17.542
Robin, where are you
going? That's not safe!

15:20.667 --> 15:22.708
Come on. Are you crazy?

15:23.000 --> 15:25.125
This is dangerous.
We can't talk here.

15:25.375 --> 15:26.833
You've met someone else?

15:27.917 --> 15:31.042
- I knew you'd think that.
- You have. You're lying.

15:31.292 --> 15:32.708
I haven't. Jesus!

15:33.000 --> 15:37.042
So after 16 fine years,
why a divorce?

15:38.458 --> 15:40.875
It's me. I'm confused.

15:41.083 --> 15:44.042
I want a different life, to
go in a different direction.

15:44.292 --> 15:46.458
- Confused? Then see a doctor.
- I did.

15:46.750 --> 15:49.000
Well, that's news!

15:49.208 --> 15:52.750
What other surprises
you got in store?

15:53.125 --> 15:54.917
This wasn't an easy decision.

15:55.625 --> 15:57.208
You've met someone.

15:57.417 --> 15:59.583
No-one just ups and goes.

15:59.792 --> 16:01.958
You know, we got
married so young.

16:02.167 --> 16:03.958
- Never time for living!
- Change your life how?

16:04.167 --> 16:05.958
All we know
is each other!

16:06.167 --> 16:08.500
So who do you want
to explore, Allison?

16:08.708 --> 16:10.083
Why Allison?

16:10.292 --> 16:13.875
- Your hands touched in the car.
- I don't believe this!

16:14.292 --> 16:16.875
And you didn't pull yours away!

16:17.083 --> 16:18.708
You had an affair with Allison!

16:18.917 --> 16:20.750
- Our neighbour!
- Not an affair!

16:21.000 --> 16:23.792
- You slept with her!
- That's why I want a divorce!

16:24.000 --> 16:25.583
To marry Allison?

16:26.583 --> 16:29.000
I can't be dishonest,
and I have been...

16:29.500 --> 16:31.417
and I don't want to do it.

16:33.708 --> 16:36.042
- Who else?
- Nobody else.

16:38.583 --> 16:40.375
Lee, tell me...

16:41.250 --> 16:43.583
now we're clearing the air.

16:43.875 --> 16:45.750
I won't get angry.

16:46.042 --> 16:47.375
Lee, come on.

16:49.417 --> 16:50.958
Let's clear the air.

16:51.208 --> 16:52.958
I won't get angry.

16:54.417 --> 16:55.708
Aren't you cold?

16:55.958 --> 16:57.542
We're clearing the air.

16:57.792 --> 16:59.708
I'm not gonna get angry.

17:03.708 --> 17:05.000
Sheila...

17:06.375 --> 17:07.458
Sheila?

17:09.583 --> 17:12.291
You lowlife
motherfucker!

17:12.541 --> 17:14.958
- I can't talk to you!
- My best friend, Sheila!

17:15.166 --> 17:18.500
It's not about women. I'm
depressed about my whole life.

17:18.750 --> 17:19.958
Your life with me?

17:20.166 --> 17:22.583
I hate these stupid
travel pieces!

17:22.791 --> 17:25.916
I tried to talk to you before,
but you're so high-strung.

17:26.166 --> 17:28.500
I mean, we
can't talk!

17:28.750 --> 17:30.958
It's over, you know?
I'm not happy!

17:35.000 --> 17:36.792
Robin, are you okay?

17:38.000 --> 17:39.750
Robin, are you okay?

17:40.625 --> 17:41.500
No.

17:42.083 --> 17:43.583
But I will be.

18:50.458 --> 18:52.292
Do you try to shock people?

18:52.708 --> 18:56.750
One of my best collections.
I'm pleased how it turned out.

19:01.500 --> 19:03.708
I'd love to talk
about this location.

19:03.917 --> 19:05.875
We'll definitely get together.

19:06.083 --> 19:07.625
It's an inspired idea!

19:11.917 --> 19:14.125
The skyline enhances
my collection.

19:14.667 --> 19:16.167
The colour's great, isn't it?

19:16.375 --> 19:18.917
A fantastic backdrop
for your work.

19:19.542 --> 19:22.208
It'd be great to talk
more about this.

19:22.417 --> 19:23.833
Come next week.

19:24.042 --> 19:26.292
We'll have lunch and I'll
show you round.

19:26.500 --> 19:27.833
Can we talk more now?

19:28.042 --> 19:30.833
- It'd help me with the details.
- Sure, no problem.

20:02.375 --> 20:03.667
Nice car.

20:04.708 --> 20:07.250
Thanks. Want
to drive it?

20:07.500 --> 20:09.917
- Because it's a terrific...
- Is it yours?

20:10.208 --> 20:11.792
Sure. What am I, a car thief?

20:12.000 --> 20:13.833
It's an Aston Martin.

20:14.708 --> 20:16.792
You're welcome, come on.

