- Lie in front of these people?

38:44.292 --> 38:45.917
- I'm sorry.
- That's okay.

38:46.125 --> 38:47.500
No, I lost control.

38:47.708 --> 38:49.958
I guess you're still
in love with him.

38:50.167 --> 38:51.458
I guess I am.

38:51.750 --> 38:53.208
Good night.

38:54.667 --> 38:56.292
Well, think about what I said.

38:56.500 --> 38:59.208
- About what?
- About coming to work for me.

38:59.750 --> 39:01.375
That's a fantasy.

39:02.750 --> 39:04.167
You're bright. You'd learn.

39:04.625 --> 39:08.333
My company's growing.
You could grow with us.

39:09.708 --> 39:11.292
Too inhibited.

39:11.708 --> 39:14.458
- That's a shame.
- I'm sorry.

39:15.000 --> 39:16.167
Good night.

39:26.917 --> 39:30.625
- Did you like the movie?
- I hate Papadakis.

39:30.833 --> 39:33.083
One cliché after another.

39:33.583 --> 39:37.250
When you see these scripts,
it's so depressing.

39:39.042 --> 39:41.417
Were you upset about
the run-in with your ex?

39:42.333 --> 39:45.250
She's an hysteric.
I'm lucky I got out.

39:45.542 --> 39:48.042
Tonight was proof
positive, if I needed proof.

39:48.375 --> 39:50.292
Sounds like you're
protesting too much.

39:50.500 --> 39:53.750
No, my class reunion was
the defining moment for me.

39:54.083 --> 39:56.000
<i>- How's that?
- A class reunion last year.</i>

39:56.208 --> 39:57.667
<i>Take my advice. Don't do it.</i>

39:57.875 --> 40:00.375
Doris, Doris! How are you?

40:00.625 --> 40:02.208
