40:04.917 --> 40:07.417
- What are you up to?
- I work in imports.

40:07.625 --> 40:09.833
- What are you doing?
- I write for a travel magazine.

40:10.042 --> 40:11.458
Get to travel for free?

40:11.667 --> 40:15.292
Free, yeah, tell me about it.
We crash-landed in Dubrovnik!

40:15.500 --> 40:16.667
Eddie, Eddie!

40:16.875 --> 40:18.375
- Look what the cat dragged in.
- Nice to see you.

40:18.583 --> 40:20.458
This is Lenore, my wife.

40:21.167 --> 40:22.458
What are you up to?

40:22.667 --> 40:25.583
We've got four kids.
