for a sandwich?

48:42.292 --> 48:43.667
Of course, Mary...?

48:43.917 --> 48:46.458
- Can I see you in my office?
- Just a minute. Mary...

48:46.667 --> 48:47.917
Margaret, I'm so sorry...

48:48.125 --> 48:50.917
The attorney is
expecting a call...

48:51.125 --> 48:53.333
- Hi, I'm Dawn Dawson.
- Dawn Dawson?

48:53.542 --> 48:56.792
The teenage obese acrobat.
I had an appointment today.

48:57.667 --> 48:59.667
The teenage obese acrobat, today?

49:00.250 --> 49:02.375
- You said the 14th.
- Our "Overweight Achievers."

49:02.583 --> 49:04.583
Oh my God! I gave
