49:04.792 --> 49:06.417
- You said the 14th.
- I am so sorry.

49:06.625 --> 49:08.917
Excuse me, the
skinheads are here.

49:09.125 --> 49:10.875
Green Room's
getting crowded.

49:11.083 --> 49:13.917
How about the lounge?
