49:28.708 --> 49:31.042
- Come here.
- I'm so sorry.

49:31.250 --> 49:32.875
I screwed up. I'm so sorry.

49:33.125 --> 49:36.250
I've been watching you run
up and down all morning...

49:36.500 --> 49:38.542
and I can't take my eyes off you.

49:38.792 --> 49:42.208
I can't get the
weekend in Bermuda...

49:42.458 --> 49:43.333
out of my mind.

49:43.542 --> 49:44.958
There's lots to do.

49:45.167 --> 49:47.250
Priorities. Never
confuse...

49:47.625 --> 49:49.125
priorities.

49:49.833 --> 49:51.042
Oh my God!

49:53.167 --> 49:55.792
I'm Professor Benz. We're
here for the taping.

49:56.000 --> 49:57.875
I'm sorry, there's
been a mistake.

49:58.083 --> 50:01.667
Sorry. "Overweight Achievers"
is next week.

50:02.250 --> 50:03.250
Sorry.

50:03.833 --> 50:06.292
- Who are you?
- Lou DeMarco.

50:06.542 --> 50:07.500
Who?

50:07.917 --> 50:11.500
Uncle to Tony Lipriano from
the Genovese family, that's who.

50:11.792 --> 50:14.792
Our "Cosa Nostra"
show is next week.

50:15.125 --> 50:16.208
