You're with William Morris?
Don't make me laugh!

50:32.708 --> 50:35.542
Where are the bagels? Have the
skinheads eaten them all?

50:39.208 --> 50:41.333
Could you interview this
professional woman...

50:41.708 --> 50:44.125
for the panel on lovemaking
next Tuesday?

50:44.333 --> 50:46.417
What's the show
called?

50:46.625 --> 50:49.667
"Working Girls Born in
Manhattan." I'm Nina.

50:49.875 --> 50:51.792
Nina, right. Great.

50:52.375 --> 50:53.333
Bye.

50:53.542 --> 50:55.667
So you're a hooker.

50:56.125 --> 50:57.458
Yeah, that's right.

50:59.083 --> 51:01.667
Hey, Tony, you
finally got here.

51:01.917 --> 51:03.417
Traffic that bad?

51:03.708 --> 51:06.458
Told you it'd be heavy
traffic. I knew it.

51:06.750 --> 51:10.125
Grandma, look who's here!
Your favourite grandson!

51:10.375 --> 51:12.750
- Hi Tony.
- Hi, Grandma.

51:14.083 --> 51:16.000
God, we were waiting for you.

51:16.250 --> 51:18.792
- Where have you been?
- This is Robin, everybody.

51:19.125 --> 51:20.167
How do you do?

51:21.833 --> 51:23.500
This is my sister, Iris.

51:25.542 --> 51:27.667
- Tony's a real doll.
- I know.

51:27.958 --> 51:29.792
He got us this house.
Show her the house.

51:30.000 --> 51:31.292
Mom, will you stop it?

51:31.708 --> 51:35.708
But there's a waiting list to get
Grandpa into the nursing home.

51:36.250 --> 51:39.458
It's the only home I trust.
The others are toilets.

51:39.667 --> 51:43.458
