52:08.333 --> 52:11.458
There's a 6-month waiting
list for this restaurant.

52:11.667 --> 52:14.875
- I'll have Mary make the call.
- As long as it's convenient.

52:15.083 --> 52:17.000
Tony's nobody's fool.

52:17.208 --> 52:20.292
When will you get my Knick's
season tickets upgraded?

52:20.500 --> 52:22.542
What am I, Don
Corleone here?

52:23.167 --> 52:25.375
Not for me, brother,
for your nephew.

52:25.667 --> 52:27.833
Ricky! Come here.

52:28.333 --> 52:30.833
Tell Grandma who came
and spoke at your school.

52:31.125 --> 52:33.750
- A guest speaker?
- Yeah, John Brennan.

52:34.042 --> 52:36.167
- Very nice!
- The hostage guy.

52:36.375 --> 52:38.125
- You don't know John Brennan?
- The hostage, Grandma.

52:38.333 --> 52:41.208
- You remember!
- No, I never heard of him.

52:41.458 --> 52:45.167
They hijacked his plane and
held him hostage for months.

52:45.375 --> 52:46.500
