52:46.708 --> 52:50.125
- Yes she does. Dad, you remember?
- Sure. It was in the papers.

52:50.333 --> 52:53.000
In the papers, on the
television, everything.

52:53.208 --> 52:56.708
They released him and he got this
hero's welcome. He's famous!

52:56.958 --> 52:59.542
